title: Chipotle
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fast food chain where you could customize your order (salads, tacos, burritos, bowls) and request no cheese/dairy. Some of its locations (including this one) offer a soyfrito filling that's made from soy protein. The white beans used to be cooked with bacon but are currently vegan; please confirm with staff.
